lead_paragraph: Todd Bowles made a strong statement about his happiness with the team’s start when he declared that Ryan Fitzpatrick would be his starting quarterback even when Geno Smith returns from injury.

headline.main: Philadelphia Eagles at New York Jets Preview: Fitzpatrick Settles In
